schools.name: Alfred B. Nobel Charter Middle School

data.description: Beautiful home situated in one of the most desirable areas of Northridge!! Property is only a few minutes away from California State University Northridge. You will not find a property in the city of Northridge with a living space of 2,378 at listed price. This home  features 4 bedrooms, 1 den that can be used as a 5th bedroom, and 3 baths. Move in ready interior features custom kitchen cabinets, spacious dining area and central air conditioning. The backyard is a one of a kind custom experience with an extravagant pool that provides a family the ultimate outdoor entertainment. Property has Solar Panels that will be paid off by the seller at close of escrow. The roof was completely replaced when the solar panels were installed. Garage was converted to a living space. Per seller, the garage was converted to a living space with permits. Property is located close to freeways, restaurants, and shopping centers. This property is a must see!!
